title: Bobby Got Eddie An Awesome Birthday Gift + Kelsea Ballerini Talks About Ed Sheeran Writing On Her Walls + Mike D Wants To Drive To Pick Up Girlfriend
itunes:title: Bobby Got Eddie An Awesome Birthday Gift + Kelsea Ballerini Talks About Ed Sheeran Writing On Her Walls + Mike D Wants To Drive To Pick Up Girlfriend
description:
It’s Producer Eddie’s birthday tomorrow so Bobby got him a gift Eddie had been hinting about, but wasn’t able to buy for himself. Kelsea Ballerini stopped by for 'The Friday Morning Conversation' to talk about her new album out today, writing with Ed Sheeran and her duet with Kenny Chesney. Plus, Mike D wants to drive from Nashville to Austin, TX to pick up his girlfriend so they can be quarantined together!
